{
  "stem": "11801.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, I-- the orphanage looked up for me the names of some Jewish organizations.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They found out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She stayed with me overnight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They gave us a room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, they fixed up a room with two beds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were very kind and made some inquiries.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I took her then to this organization, which gave her some money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was able to find a little room in a loft somewhere.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they gave her a little money for food, but not really a lot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there were all kinds of places that fed the refugees.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I guess you would call them soup kitchens today.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So she used to go to the soup kitchens and eat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I remember going with her to pick up some clothes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were these places with clothes all-- you know, with just masses of clothing all mixed up, I mean, shoes all mixed up.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But you know, this was nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was-- didn't faze my mother at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It bothered me a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It bothered me, not, not because [LAUGHS] it was difficult to find the clothes that fit her.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But it bothered me to see all these people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there was-- I, I recall hundreds of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Looked so sad, and looked so emaciated, and who looked sickly, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who, who behaved in, in strange ways that I didn't really want to be involved with.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And at long last, I had somewhere to go on the one Sunday a month when we were allowed to go out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the first few months, my mother didn't have any money.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
